eutros.multiblocktweaker.crafttweaker

Class CustomMultiblock

  • java.lang.Object
    • eutros.multiblocktweaker.crafttweaker.CustomMultiblock

  • public class CustomMultiblock
extends java.lang.Object
    A representation of a custom GregTech Multiblock.

    This is best used for easy access to the recipe map.

    Use this to set any custom working functions.

    See Also:
    MultiblockBuilder, IUpdateFunction, IUpdateWorktableFunction, ISetupRecipeFunction, ICompleteRecipeFunction, IRecipePredicate
    ZenClass:
    mods.gregtech.multiblock.Multiblock
